Hey Friends!

Tuscumbia Yearbook is still for sale! With the year being cut short, we know that a lot of kiddos are bummed! This yearbook will be filled with all the great times we have shared this year so that we can all remember the good times for years to come! With QR codes that link to special videos and photos not otherwise seen and articles spotlights from our yearbook student staff, you don‚Äôt want to miss out!

Order forms were sent home prior to the buildings being shut down and more are in the office! Just ask the staff for one on Tuesdays when you pick up homework! Or order online!

We appreciate you and your support in our efforts to capture all the memories from the 2019-2020 school year!

This semester our students are working on improving their photography skills. Each week they will be submitting their best candid shot they took that week. The LA I, II, and III classes will be voting on which candid is their favorite. We will be displaying the winning photo each week right here on ROAR TV. Check back each week to see who will be chosen for the Candid of the Week!

This week Keagan Rayhart took the winning photo. His unique viewpoint gave him the edge. Good job Keagan!
